spec_data.Name: perl-NetPacket-SpanningTree
spec_data.Description:
NetPacket::SpanningTree provides a set of routines for assembling and
disassembling packets using the IEEE standard Spanning Tree Protocol.
Spanning Tree is a layer 2 protocol defined by the IEEE 802.1D
specification.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 02:46:10 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Assemble and disassemble IEEE 802.1D Spanning Tree protocol packets
